name: Tori Black
description:
This my first textual inversion, and depicts Tori Black.

Version 1 is trained only on her face, and I've found it difficult to induce models to give her a body. I'm working on a version 2 which will include her body.

I trained it on SD 1.5 and it generates the best faces when using that model.

I hope you like it!

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description: This was trained on 15 photographs of Tori Black's face and doesn't include her body. The TI was set up with 50 vectors.
